This is because, since the graph is undirected, there's only one way to traverse from the root node to any given leaf node (the path will be unique). And, assuming each node in the graph is connected, there are n - 1 total paths that can be traversed (where n is the number of nodes). Therefore, the total time complexity of this algorithm will be O(n - 1) or just O(n).
